ouple-dead-murder-suicide-san-ysidro%2F14231829%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthorities%20found%20the%20pair%20several%20days%20later%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dead%20inside%20their%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnij.ojp.gov%2Ftopics%2Farticles%2Fmurder-suicide-families%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20murder-suicide%20occurs%20when%20one%20intimate%20partner%20%E2%80%94%20often%20male%20%E2%80%94%20kills%20the%20other%20partner%20and%20then%20takes%20their%20own%20life.%20When%20children%20are%20also%20killed%20in%20the%20act%2C%20the%20murder-suicide%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20familicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMurder-suicide%20perpetrators%20are%20typically%20middle-aged%20men%20with%20access%20to%20firearms%2C%20experts%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20rarity%20of%20murder-suicides%2C%20the%20US%20does%20not%20keep%20an%20official%20database%20tracking%20their%20frequency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Alexander%20Tsai%2C%20a%20board-certified%20staff%20psychiatrist%20at%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20and%20associate%20professor%20of%20psychiatry%20at%20Harvard%20Medical%20School%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20murder-suicides%20are%20difficult%20to%20study%20for%20that%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rate%20is%20fewer%20than%20one%20per%20100%2C000%20people%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETsai%20said%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20typically%20men%20in%20their%2040s%20or%2050s%2C%20and%20the%20precipitating%20event%20is%20often%20a%20separation%20or%20divorce.%20Unlike%20other%20types%20of%20violent%20perpetrators%2C%20such%20as%20mass%20shooters%2C%20murder-suicides%20are%20often%20committed%20by%20people%20who%20are%20employed%20full-time%2C%20Tsai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20%26quot%3Bnot%20people%20in%20their%20basement%2C%20on%20Twitter%2C%20going%20down%20rabbit%20holes%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%26quot%3B%20Tsai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Institute%20of%20Justice%20has%20identified%20four%20common%20characteristics%20in%20murder-suicides%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Eprior%20history%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Eaccess%20to%20firearms%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Ethreats%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3Eand%20a%20prior%20history%20of%20mental%20illness%20or%20substance%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20particularly%20emphasized%20the%20role%20of%20guns%20in%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20murder-suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Institute%20of%20Justice%20said%20that%20out%20of%20591%20murder-suicides%2C%2092%25%20were%20committed%20with%20a%20gun%2C%20and%20states%20with%20less%20restrictive%20gun%20laws%20have%20up%20to%20eight%20times%20the%20rate%20of%20murder-suicides%20as%20states%20with%20more%20restrictive%20gun%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20overwhelming%20amount%20of%20murder-suicides%20involve%20guns%2C%26quot%3B%20Tsai%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20these%20acts%20that%20are%20committed%20out%20of%20impulsivity%2C%20there's%20really%20no%20turning%20back%20with%20a%20firearm%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0whereas%20if%20you%20had%20a%20baseball%20bat%20%E2%80%A6%20there%20is%20some%20turning%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Slutkin%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20Intervention%20Development%20Unit%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Cure%20Violence%20Global%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20many%20forms%20of%20violence%20have%20been%20worsening%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20worsen%20in%202024%20and%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20particularly%2C%20communities%20lack%20systems%20to%20interrupt%20violent%20events%20beyond%20law-enforcement%20agencies%2C%20he%20said.%20Slutkin%20said%20part%20of%20solving%20the%20problem%20will%20involve%20outreach%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20not%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoms%20and%20friends%20don't%20want%20to%20call%20police%20on%20their%20family%20and%20friends.%20You%20need%20a%20different%20system%E2%80%A6%20a%20violence-interrupter%20system%2C%20like%20firefighters%2C%20but%20they're%20trained%20differently%20on%20how%20to%20cool%20down%20potential%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmurder-suicides-across-us-december-problem-getting-worse-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704053409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6591c80c1c5c7b8c9a0d1bbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmurder-suicides-across-us-december-problem-getting-worse-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suspected%20murder-suicides%20or%20familicides%20occurred%20in%20Arizona%2C%20California%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Texas%20in%20December.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22horecchio%40businessinsider.com%20(Haven%20Orecchio-Egresitz%2CMichelle%20Mark)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmurder-suicides-across-us-december-problem-getting-worse-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226-year-old%20killed%20after%20rape%20bid%2C%20sniffer%20dog%20helps%20nab%20watchman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704053243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106426484%2Cimgsize-238079.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F6-year-old-killed-after-rape-bid-sniffer-dog-helps-nab-watchman%2Farticleshow%2F106426472.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Disqualify%20BJP%20candidate%20sworn%20in%20as%20Raj%20mantri%