%3EiCloud%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20find%20your%20Apple%20ID%20and%20set%20a%20new%20password%20in%20just%20a%20few%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20your%20Apple%20ID%20under%20the%20settings%20menu.%20Your%20Apple%20ID%20is%20the%20email%20address%20you%20used%20when%20you%20created%20your%20Apple%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%2C%20open%20the%20settings%20app%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%3C%2Fa%3E%20(or%20settings%20menu%20on%20a%20computer)%2C%20tap%20your%20account%2C%20tap%20%26quot%3BSign-In%20%26amp%3B%20Security%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20hit%20%26quot%3BChange%20Password%26quot%3B%20and%20follow%20the%20steps%20as%20shown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20use%20Apple's%20iForgot%20site%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20locked%20out%20of%20all%20of%20your%20devices%20and%20can't%20recall%20which%20password%20is%20associated%20with%20your%20Apple%20ID%2C%20then%20you%20have%20a%20slightly%20larger%20problem%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20solution%3A%20use%20Apple's%20iForgot%20site%20to%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGo%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiforgot.apple.com%2Fpassword%2Fverify%2Fappleid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiforgot.apple.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ideally%2C%20you%20will%20be%20doing%20this%20on%20a%20Mac%20associated%20with%20your%20account.%20If%20you%20can't%20do%20that%2C%20make%20sure%20an%20iPhone%20associated%20with%20your%20account%20is%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20iForgot%20site%2C%20enter%20the%20mobile%20phone%20number%20associated%20with%20your%20Apple%20account%20along%20with%20the%20captcha%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen.%20Then%20click%20%26quot%3BContinue%26quot%3B%20and%20follow%20the%20prompt%20on%20the%20next%20page%20to%20enter%20your%20Apple%20ID%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20click%20%26quot%3BContinue%2C%26quot%3B%20prompts%20will%20automatically%20be%20sent%20to%20your%20phone%20and%20computer%20asking%20if%20it's%20OK%20to%20use%20one%20of%20those%20devices%20to%20reset%20your%20password.%20Click%20or%20tap%20to%20give%20permission%2C%20then%20follow%20the%20prompts%20to%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%2C%20which%20will%20end%2C%20for%20now%2C%20with%20you%20waiting%20for%20an%20account%20recovery%20email%20from%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20check%20my%20iForgot%20Apple%20status%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESubmitting%20a%20password%20change%20request%20via%20Apple's%20iForgot%20site%20isn't%20all%20that%20complicated%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20quite%20as%20rapid-fire%20as%20you%20may%20be%20used%20to%20in%20our%20digital%20world.%20In%20fact%2C%20per%20Apple%2C%20it%20may%20take%20up%20to%2072%20hours%20for%20your%20account%20recovery%20email%20to%20be%20sent%20after%20your%20request.%20(And%20some%20people%20have%20reported%20waiting%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20for%20the%20email.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20suffer%20through%20the%20interminable%20wait%2C%20at%20least%20you%20can%20check%20on%20the%20status%20of%20your%20recovery%20process.%20Go%20to%20the%20iForgot%20site%2C%20enter%20your%20Apple%20ID%2C%20and%20click%20through%20to%20see%20where%20you%20are%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20Apple%20recover%20your%20Apple%20ID%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Apple%20ID%20recovery%20process%20could%20take%20seconds%2C%20not%20days%3B%20Apple%20has%20all%20of%20your%20information%20securely%20stored%20and%20can%20share%20with%20you%20the%20option%20to%20create%20a%20new%20password%20and%20resume%20normal%20use%20of%20your%20account%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2072-hour%20delay%20is%20a%20security%20feature%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20deterrent%20that%20makes%20using%20the%20recovery%20process%20to%20steal%20someone%20else's%20account%20credentials%20less%20alluring%20to%20cybercriminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20am%20I%20getting%20a%20text%20to%20reset%20my%20Apple%20ID%20password%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20getting%20a%20text%20to%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%2C%20you%20are%20being%20scammed.%20In%20almost%20all%20cases%20it's%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20text%20messages%20asking%20you%20to%20reset%20a%20password%20are%20phishing%20attempts%20to%20steal%20your%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%20when%20you%20get%20a%20text%20on%20a%20trusted%20device%20sharing%20a%20code%20as%20part%20of%20two-step%20verification.%20That%20process%20is%20legitimate%2C%20assuming%20it%20was%20you%20who%20requested%20the%20login%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20recovery%20mode%20delete%20everything%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecovering%20your%20Apple%20ID%20and%20password%20is%20different%20than%20using%20recovery%20mode%20on%20an%20iPhone.%20Very%20different%2C%20in%20fact.%20Whereas%20the%20former%20simply%20allows%20you%20to%20begin%20using%20your%20Apple%20account%20as%20usual%20again%2C%20the%20latter%20will%20delete%20all%20of%20the%20data%20stored%20on%20a%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20recovery%20mode%20to%20get%20back%20into%20an%20iPhone%20(or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-apple-ipads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPad%3C%2Fa%3E)%20from%20which%20you%20have%20been%20locked%20out%20wipes%20that%20device%20clean%20of%20photos%2C%20apps%2C%20games%2C%20and%20more%2C%20restoring%20it%20to%20factory%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iforgot%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704048181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ec56bec62ab5daf7f7d4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22