%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-vintage-photos-history-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20McDonald's%20to%20Burger%20King%2C%20these%20fast-food%20chains%20used%20to%20look%20drastically%20different.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22emcdowell%40insider.com%20(Erin%20McDowell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A117%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-vintage-photos-history-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Pakistan%20Defeats%20India%2C%20It's%20An%20Upset...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir%20On%20Cricket%20Rivalry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20on-field%20rivalry%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20intense%20battles%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cricket.%20The%20two%20teams%20have%20not%20played%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%20around%20a%20decade%20due%20to%20political%20tensions%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20their%20matches%20in%20international%20or%20continental%20competitions%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20highly-anticipated%20encounters%20in%20the%20calendar.%20Last%20time%20when%20these%20two%20teams%20faced%20each%20other%20was%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20India%20were%20able%20to%20extend%20their%20unbeaten%20run%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20tournament.%20Former%20India%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20that%20India%20are%20currently%20%26quot%3Bfar%20superior%26quot%3B%20in%20comparison%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20balance%20in%20the%20rivalry%20is%20not%20same%20as%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20has%20dominated%20India%20a%20lot%20of%20times.%20Currently%2C%20if%20you%20see%20the%20level%20of%20both%20teams%2C%20India%20is%20far%20superior%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20all%20three%20formats.%20If%20Pakistan%20defeats%20India%20it's%20an%20upset%2C%20if%20India%20defeats%20Pakistan%2C%20it's%20very%20much%20given%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20went%20unbeaten%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20before%20they%20were%20eventually%20defeated%20by%20Australia%20in%20the%20final.%20Gambhir%20said%20that%20the%20rivalry%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20top%20one%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20and%20he%20believes%20that%20it%20has%20even%20surpassed%20the%20India-Pakistan%20cricket%20rivalry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20Australia%2C%20from%20a%20cricketing%20point%20of%20view%2C%20is%20a%20top%20rivalry.%20If%20you%20ask%20a%20cricket%20fan%20what%20is%20the%20actual%20rivalry%2C%20they%20will%20also%20say%20India%20and%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversies.%20Gambhir%20is%20well%20known%20for%20his%20fiery%20comments%20and%20straightforward%20analysis%20which%20sometimes%20leads%20to%20conversations%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20Q%26amp%3BA%20session%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20a%20fan%20ended%20up%20asking%20Gambhir%20why%20he%20makes%20such%20'controversial%20statements'.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20you%20always%20give%20so%20much%20controversial%20statements%3F%20%23AskGG%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%20In%20response%2C%20Gambhir%20came%20up%20with%20his%20blunt%20style%20of%20answering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%20what%20I%20feel.%20You%20should%20think%20who%20benefits%20from%20the%20controversies!%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704030480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkq6tcivo_india-pakistan-match_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fif-pakistan-defeats-india-its-an-upset-gautam-gambhir-on-crick