ncy%20in%20hotels%2C%20said%20Shimla%20Hotel%20and%20Tourism%20Stakeholders%20Association%20president%20MK%20Seth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20occupancy%20is%20about%2050-60%20per%20cent%20which%20is%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20last%2040%20years%20and%20even%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20New%20Year%20tourist%20rush%20was%20more%20than%20this%2C%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20follow%20'%3Cem%3EAtithi%20Devo%20Bhava%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20and%20facilitate%20tourists%20and%20make%20adequate%20arrangements%20in%20all%20districts%20for%20the%20smooth%20flow%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20allowing%20food%20joints%20and%20pan%20shops%20to%20remain%20open%2024x7%2C%20he%20said%20drunk%20tourists%20will%20not%20be%20arrested%2C%20but%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20their%20hotels%20by%20the%20cops%20to%20ensure%20their%20New%20Year%20experience%20is%20not%20spoiled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unregistered%20tourism%20units%20are%20eating%20into%20the%20sales%20of%20registered%20hotels%2C%20home%20stays%20and%20other%20such%20accommodations%2C%20said%20Mr%20Seth%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20tourists%20coming%20by%20train%20and%20luxury%20buses%20are%20%26quot%3Bcaptured%26quot%3B%20by%20touts%20who%20take%20them%20to%20unregistered%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20surprised%20to%20see%20such%20a%20drop%20in%20tourist%20inflow%20when%20all%20things%20are%20favourable.%20This%20is%20the%20lowest%20occupancy%20in%20my%20living%20memory%26quot%3B%20said%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20association%20Prince%20Kukreja%2C%20hoping%20that%20the%20occupancy%20would%20pick%20up%20by%20late%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20tourists%20prefer%20isolated%20accommodations%20in%20the%20suburbs%20with%20forest%20cover%20and%20peace%2C%20and%20those%20planning%20private%20parties%20are%20also%20going%20beyond%20the%20city%2C%20said%20local%20hotelier%20Shishu%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20the%20hotels%20in%20the%20main%20town%2C%20normally%20packed%20during%20this%20time%2C%20are%20not%20packed%20to%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%207%2C600%20tourists%20vehicles%20from%20other%20states%20have%20come%20to%20Shimla%20via%20Shoghi%20barrier%20on%20the%20Shimla-Chandigarh%20Road%20from%20Saturday%20morning%20(8%20am)%20to%20Sunday%20afternoon%20(12%20pm)%2C%20SP%20Shimla%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%20Gandhi%20told%20PTI%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tourism%20stakeholders%20added%20that%20adverse%20publicity%20on%20social%20media%20and%20some%20electronic%20channels%20regarding%20traffic%20jams%20diverted%20tourists%20to%20other%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20Met%20office%20predicted%20snowfall%20and%20rainfall%20at%20isolated%20places%20in%20high-and-mid%20hills%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20as%20a%20fresh%20Western%20Disturbance%20lies%20over%20the%20Himalayan%20region.%20However%2C%20no%20snowfall%20was%20witnessed%20in%20the%20key%20tourist%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704026340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffl5dss4g_shimla-_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshimla-sees-record-40-year-drop-in-hotel-occupancy-on-new-years-eve-4775582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prediction%20of%20weekend%20snow%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20directions%20to%20not%20be%20harsh%20with%20drunk%20revelers%20on%20New%20Year%20failed%20to%20woo%20tourists%20to%20Shimla%20which%20recorded%20a%2050-60%20per%20cent%20occupancy%20-%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lowest%20in%20the%20last%2040%20years%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs