nagariya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Farvind-panagariya-ex-advisor-to-pm-modi-is-indias-new-finance-commission-head-11704014720605.html%5C%22%3Eappointed%20economist%20Arvind%20Panagariya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20a%20former%20advisor%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20new%20Finance%20Commission%20which%20will%20look%20into%20federal%20taxes%20shared%20with%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanagariya%20will%20be%20the%20head%20of%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20while%20Ritvik%20Ranjanam%20Pandey%20will%20be%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20commission.%20Panagariya%20served%20as%20the%20first%20vice-chairman%20of%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20from%20January%202015%20to%20August%202027%2C%20in%20the%20rank%20of%20a%20cabinet%20minister.%20He%20is%20a%20former%20chief%20economist%20of%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%2C%20held%20key%20posts%20at%20World%20Bank%2C%20IMF%20and%20UNCTAD%2C%20and%20also%20taught%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Finance%20Commission%20is%20likely%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20October%2031%2C%202025.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Centre%20shares%2042%25%20of%20federal%20taxes%20with%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fbjps-lies-are-the-strongest-kharge-2830524%5C%22%3Ehit%20out%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20eve%2C%20alleging%20that%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20lies%20are%20the%20strongest%E2%80%9D%2C%20citing%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20failed%20promise%20of%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20by%202022%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1741293228081688962%5C%22%3EKharge%20said%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi-ji%2C%20today%20is%20the%20last%20day%20of%202023.%20You%20said%20that%20by%202022%20every%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20income%20will%20double%2C%20every%20Indian%20will%20have%20a%20house%20and%2024%C3%977%20electricity%2C%20The%20economy%20will%20become%20USD%20five%20trillion.%20All%20this%20did%20not%20happen%20but%20every%20Indian%20knows%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20lies%20are%20the%20strongest!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1741322333762044287%5C%22%3Eattacked%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20shielding%20powerful%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20women%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20him%2C%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20Olympian%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20returning%20her%20Khel%20Ratna%20and%20Arjuna%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20daughter%20of%20the%20country%2C%20self-respect%20comes%20first%2C%20any%20other%20medal%20or%20honour%20comes%20after%20that.%20Does%20the%20price%20of%20%E2%80%98political%20benefits%E2%80%99%20received%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98proclaimed%20Bahubali%E2%80%99%20exceed%20the%20tears%20of%20these%20brave%20daughters%3F%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20the%20guardian%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20it%20hurts%20to%20see%20such%20cruelty%20on%20his%20part.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20media%20chief%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20for%20delaying%20the%20decennial%20census%2C%20which%20was%20due%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhagwant%20Mann%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rejection%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20tableau%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20soon%20became%20a%20political%20row%20between%20the%20AAP%20and%20BJP%2C%20when%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20AAP%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20lash%20out%20at%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMann%20said%20that%20the%20tableau%20highlighted%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Rajguru%2C%20Sukhdev%2C%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%2C%20Udham%20Singh%20and%20others%20and%20they%20will%20not%20be%20displayed%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Crejected%20category%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20our%20heroes%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20respect%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhagwant-mann-aap-republic-day-parade-bhagwant-manns-rejected-category-remark-amid-row-over-punjab-tableau-4775209%5C%22%3ENDTV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20after%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20tableau%20did%20not%20make%20the%20cut%2C%20the%20Union%20defence%20ministry%20had%20written%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20accept%20the%20tableau%20during%20Bharat%20Parv%20from%20January%2023%20to%2031.%20However%2C%20Mann%20opposed%20the%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20will%20not%20send%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20tableau%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Crejected%20category%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20government%20sources%20dismissed%20such%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdiscrimination%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fpunjab-tableau-rejection-rotation-system-process-government-selection-delhi-2024-republic-day-parade-2482492-2023-12-31%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%20reported.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETehreek%20E%20Hurriyat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20declared%20Kashmiri%20political%20party%20Tehreek-e-Hurriyat%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9CUnlawful%20Association%E2%80%9D%20for%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sections%20of%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20home%20ministry%20claimed%20that%20the%20organisation%20had%20been%20advocating%20separatism%20and%20establishment%20of%20Islamist%20rule%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTehreek-e-Hurriyat%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20(TeH)%20has%20been%20declared%20an%20%E2%80%98Unlawful%20Association%E2%80%99%20under%20UAPA.%20The%20outfit%20is%20involved%20in%20forbidden%20activities%20to%20separate%20J%26amp%3BK%20from%20India%20and%20establish%20Islamic%20rule.%20The%20group%20is%20found%20spreading%20anti-India%20propaganda%20and%20continuing%20terror%20activities%20to%20fuel%20secessionism%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20Ji%E2%80%99s%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20terrorism%2C%20any%20individual%20or%20organization%20found%20involved%20in%20anti-India%20activities%20will%20be%20thwarted%20forthwith%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeH%20was%20once%20helmed%20by%20Syed%20Ali%20Shah%20Geelani%20and%20has%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20past%20to%20facilitate%20talks%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia-Ukraine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20what%20Russia%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20attack%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20city%20of%20Belgorod%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Russia%20launched%20fresh%20drone%20strikes%20against%20Ukraine%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20reported%20that%20Iranian-made%20%E2%80%9CShahed%E2%80%9D%20drones%20targeted%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20north-eastern%20city%20of%20Kharkiv.%20Many%20civilian%20buildings%20of%20Kharikiv%20were%20reported%20to%20be%20damaged%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20Belgorod%20killed%20at%20least%2022%20people%20while%20many%20were%20left%20injured%2C%20in%20what%20was%20the%20deadliest%20attack%20on%20Russia%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20February%202022.%20Moscow%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20used%20the%20controversial%20cluster%20munitions%2C%20and%20told%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20that%20Kyiv%20had%20targeted%20a%20sports%20centre%2C%20an%20ice%20rink%2C%20and%20a%20university%2C%20with%20Russian%20envoy%20Vasily%20Nebenzya%20calling%20the%20attack%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%2C%20indiscriminate%20attack%20against%20a%20civilian%20target%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kharkiv%20mayor%20Ihor%20Therekov%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20Russians%20want%20to%20intimidate%20our%20city%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20scared.%E2%80%9D%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20allies%20countered%20that%20responsibility%20ultimately%20lay%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20for%20invading%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704025856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02171144%2FDInhsc0V4AAeE7z.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftoday-in-the-news-december-31%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Panagariya%20is%20the%20new%20Finance%20Commission%20head%2C%20Congress%20hits%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20over%20failed%20promises%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftoday-in-the-news-december-31%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Feisty%20Journalist%20and%20Documentary%20Maker%20John%20Pilger%20Passes%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31175046%2FGCq1OaeWkAADifM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20John%20Pilger%20(84)%2C%20journalist%2C%20activist%2C%20documentary%20maker%20and%20a%20legend%20for%20many%20news%20reporters%20and%20news%20analysts%2C%20is%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjohnpilger%2Fstatus%2F1741419322449215716%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eannounced%20his%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20with%20great%20sadness%20the%20family%20of%20John%20Pilger%20announce%20he%20died%20yesterday%2030%20December%202023%20in%20London%20aged%2084.%20His%20journalism%20and%20documentaries%20were%20celebrated%20around%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20to%20his%20family%20he%20was%20simply%20the%20most%20amazing%20and%20loved%20Dad%2C%20Grandad%20and%20partner.%20Rest%20In%20Peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia-born%20Pilger%20was%20adversarial%2C%20feisty%20and%20uncompromising%2C%20drawing%20praise%20and%20respect%20from%20people%20across%20the%20ideological%20fence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fbiography%5C%22%3EPilger%20was%20born%20and%20grew%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bondi%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Australia.%20His%20website%20confirms%20that%20he%20launched%20his%20first%20newspaper%20at%20Sydney%20High%20School%20and%20later%20completed%20a%20four%20year%20cadetship%20with%20Australian%20Consolidated%20Press.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20strictest%20language%20courses%20I%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDevised%20by%20a%20celebrated%2C%20literate%20editor%2C%20Brian%20Penton%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20economy%20of%20language%20and%20accuracy.%20It%20certainly%20taught%20me%20to%20admire%20writing%20that%20was%20spare%2C%20precise%20and%20free%20of%20cliches%2C%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20retreat%20into%20the%20passive%20voice%20and%20used%20adjectives%20only%20when%20absolutely%20necessary.%20I%20have%20long%20since%20slipped%20that%20leash%2C%20but%20those%20early%20disciplines%20helped%20shape%20my%20journalism%20and%20writing%20and%20my%20understanding%20of%20moving%20and%20still%20pictures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20of%20his%20Australian%20generation%2C%20Pilger%20and%20two%20colleagues%20left%20for%20Europe%20in%20the%20early%201960s.%20He%20has%20been%20mostly%20based%20in%20the%20UK%20since%201962.%20According%20to%20Pilger%E2%80%99s%20official%20website%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20set%20up%20an%20ill-fated%20freelance%20%E2%80%98agency%E2%80%99%20in%20Italy%20(with%20the%20grand%20title%20of%20%E2%80%98Interep%E2%80%99)%20and%20quickly%20went%20broke.%20Arriving%20in%20London%2C%20Pilger%20freelanced%2C%20then%20joined%20Reuters%2C%20moving%20to%20the%20London%20Daily%20Mirror%2C%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20selling%20newspaper%2C%20which%20was%20then%20changing%20to%20a%20serious%20tabloid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20chief%20foreign%20correspondent%20and%20reported%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20covering%20numerous%20wars%2C%20notably%20Vietnam.%20Still%20in%20his%20twenties%2C%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20journalist%20to%20receive%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20highest%20award%20for%20journalism%2C%C2%A0Journalist%20of%20the%20Year%C2%A0and%20was%20the%20first%20to%20win%20it%20twice.%20Moving%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20he%20reported%20the%20upheavals%20there%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20and%201970s.%20He%20marched%20with%20America%E2%80%99s%20poor%20from%20Alabama%20to%20Washington%2C%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20Martin%20Luther%20King.%20He%20was%20in%20the%20same%20room%20when%20Robert%20Kennedy%2C%20the%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20was%20assassinated%20in%20June%201968.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20in%20South%20East%20Asia%20produced%20an%20iconic%20issue%20of%20the%20London%20Mirror%2C%20devoted%20almost%20entirely%20to%20his%20world%20exclusive%20dispatches%20from%20Cambodia%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Pol%20Pot%E2%80%99s%20reign.%20The%20combined%20impact%20of%20his%C2%A0Mirror%C2%A0reports%20and%20his%20subsequent%20documentary%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fvideos%2Fyear-zero-the-silent-death-of-cambodia%5C%22%3EYear%20Zero%3A%20the%20Silent%20Death%20of%20Cambodia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raised%20almost%20%2450%20million%20for%20the%20people%20of%20that%20stricken%20country.%20Similarly%2C%20his%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fvideos%2Fdeath-of-a-nation-the-timor-conspiracy%5C%22%3E1994%20documentary%20and%20dispatches%20report%20from%20East%20Timor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20travelled%20under%20cover%2C%20helped%20galvanise%20support%20for%20the%20East%20Timorese%2C%20then%20occupied%20by%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Britain%2C%20his%20four-year%20investigation%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20group%20of%20children%20damaged%20at%20birth%20by%20the%20drug%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fvideos%2Fthalidomide-the-ninety-eight-we-forgot%5C%22%3EThalidomide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20left%20out%20of%20the%20settlement%20with%20the%20drugs%20company%2C%20resulted%20in%20a%20special%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20numerous%20documentaries%20on%20Australia%2C%20notably%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fvideos%2Fthe-secret-country-the-first-australians-fight-back%5C%22%3EThe%20Secret%20Country%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(1983)%2C%20the%20bicentary%20trilogy%C2%A0The%20Last%20Dream%C2%A0(1988)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnpilger.com%2Fvideos%2Fwelcome-to-australia%5C%22%3EWelcome%20to%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(1999)%20and%20Utopia%20(2013)%20all%20celebrated%20and%20revealed%20much%20of%20his%20own%20country%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98forgotten%20past%E2%80%99%2C%20especially%20its%20indigenous%20past%20and%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20won%20an%20American%20TV%20Academy%20Award%2C%20an%20Emmy%2C%20and%20a%20British%20Academy%20Award%2C%20a%20BAFTA%20for%20his%20documentaries%2C%20which%20have%20also%20won%20numerous%20US%20and%20European%20awards%2C%20such%20as%20as%20the%20Royal%20Television%20Society%E2%80%99s%20Best%20Documentary.%20The%20British%20Film%20Institute%20includes%20his%201979%20film%2C%20Year%20Zero%3A%20the%20Silent%20Death%20of%20Cambodia%20among%20the%20ten%20most%20important%20documentaries%20of%20the%20twentieth%20century.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20book%2C%3Cem%3E%20Hidden%20Agendas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20journalism%2C%20is%20said%20by%20some%20to%20best%20encapsulate%20his%20journalistic%20philosophy%20of%20never%20hesitating%20to%20take%20sides%20despite%20invariably%20finding%20himself%20ranged%20against%20the%20most%20powerful%20forces%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20piece%20of%20work%20by%20him%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%20online%20is%20an%20essay%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20Are%20Spartacus%E2%80%9D%3A%20Resistance%20and%20the%20unmoving%20shadow%20of%20war.%20It%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjohnmenadue.com%2Fwe-are-spartacus-resistance-and-the-unmoving-shadow-of-war%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704025291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31175046%2FGCq1OaeWkAADifM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffeisty-journalist-and-documentary-maker-john-pilger-passes-away%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia-born%20Pilger%20was%20adversarial%2C%20feisty%20and%20uncompromising%2C%20drawing%20praise%20and%20respect%20from%20people%20across%20the%20ideological%20fence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffeisty-journalist-and-documentary-maker-john-pilger-passes-away%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turned%20Away%20By%20Hospital%2C%20UP%20Woman%20Gives%20Birth%20At%20Its%20Gate%2C%20Baby%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20delivered%20her%20baby%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20District%20Women's%20Hospital%20after%20its%20staff%20allegedly%20refused%20to%20admit%20her%20as%20she%20did%20not%20have%20money%20to%20pay%20the%20fees.%20The%20baby%20died%20soon%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBudaun%20District%20Magistrate%20Manoj%20Kumar%2