0Ayodhya%20visit%2C%20by%20all%20means%2C%20was%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20of%20its%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign%2C%20and%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20its%20primary%20rival%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20similar%20but%20much%20more%20understated%20effort%20in%20its%20grand%20celebration%20of%20its%20founding%20day%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023%20in%20Nagpur%20where%20the%20party%20laid%20down%20its%20campaign%20pitch%20around%20the%20rising%20problems%20of%20unemployment%2C%20income%20inequality%2C%20price%20rise%20and%20communal%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ayodhya%20visit%20was%20planned%20to%20the%20hilt.%20He%20inaugurated%20a%20modern%20airport%20and%20railway%20station%2C%20flagged%20off%20six%20Vande%20Bharat%20and%20two%20Amrit%20Bharat%20trains%2C%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%2046%20new%20infrastructure%20development%20projects.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20hold%20a%20roadshow%20where%20he%20interacted%20with%20people%2C%20all%20curiously%20raising%20%E2%80%98Har%20Har%20Modi%E2%80%99%20slogans%20almost%20in%20unison.%20The%20other%20firebrand%20Hindutva%20leader%20in%20his%20own%20right%20%E2%80%93%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20%E2%80%93%20played%20second%20fiddle%2C%20and%20stopped%20at%20nothing%20to%20credit%20Modi%20for%20each%20and%20every%20progress%20in%20his%20own%20state%20and%20especially%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20became%20the%20leitmotif%20to%20foreground%20Modi%20as%20a%20modern-day%20deity%2C%20as%20Meera%20Manjhi%20whose%20house%20the%20prime%20minister%20visited%20to%20congratulate%20her%20on%20being%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20herself%20declared.%20In%20fact%2C%20each%20of%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20answers%20strengthened%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20how%20all%20government%20schemes%20were%20reaching%20the%20laabarthis%20without%20any%20leakage.%20Modi%20spoke%20about%20how%20he%20related%20to%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%2