D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1741102578883236122%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Modi%20Decrees%20a%20New%20Diwali%2C%20Remember%20There's%20More%20to%20Indian%20Politics%20Than%20BJP's%20Ram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-modi-decrees-a-new-diwali-remember-theres-more-to-indian-politics-than-bjps-ram%5C%22%3EAs%20Modi%20Decrees%20a%20New%20Diwali%2C%20Remember%20There%E2%80%99s%20More%20to%20Indian%20Politics%20Than%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20rally%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(development)%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evirasat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D(heritage)%20will%20take%20India%20forward%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20laying%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20campaign%20talk%20which%20promises%20to%20make%20India%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20by%202026%20and%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20appealed%20to%20all%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Bhakts%E2%80%9D%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20the%20day%20when%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20will%20be%20inaugurated%20by%20him.%20He%20asked%20everyone%20to%20light%20a%20lamp%20in%20their%20houses%2C%20and%20urged%20all%20not%20to%20crowd%20Ayodhya%20on%20the%20day%20of%20inauguration.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20waited%20for%20more%20than%20500%20years.%20Do%20wait%20for%20some%20more%20days%20and%20then%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20considering%20all%20the%20security%20aspects%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLight%20a%20Ram%20jyoti%20in%20your%20respective%20houses%20when%20the%20Lord%20reaches%20his%20new%20home%3B%20celebrate%20Diwali%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20even%20as%20he%20and%20all%20the%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20missed%20no%20opportunity%20to%20convey%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20be%20returning%20to%20his%20home%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20500%20years%20%E2%80%93%20a%20political%20instrument%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20the%20supposedly%20original%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20was%20destroyed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMughal%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20to%20build%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20at%20its%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20while%20talking%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20long%20strides%20in%20digital%20technology%20even%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preserving%20pilgrimage%20sites%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20same%20Ayodhya%20where%20Ram%20Lalla%20lived%20in%20a%20tent%20for%20years.%20But%20now%20not%20only%20has%20Ram%20got%20a%20permanent%20temple%2C%20but%20also%20four%20crore%20people%20have%20received%20their%20own%20permanent%20house%20(under%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20was%20also%20flooded%20with%20videos%20of%20how%20people%20were%20celebrating%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20and%20modern%20infrastructure%20in%20Ayodhya%20alike.%20The%20passengers%20of%20the%20first%20Indigo%20flight%20to%20Ayodhya%20were%20seen%20chanting%20Ram%20Bhajans%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Captain%20addressed%20them%20as%20being%20the%20fortunate%20one%20to%20pilot%20the%20first%20flight%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20ending%20his%20speech%20with%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Siya%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%20Supporters%20of%20Hindutva%20organised%20themselves%20to%20lash%20out%20at%20%E2%80%9CLeft%2C%20liberals%2C%20English-speaking%20seculars%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cderacinating%E2%80%9D%20Indians%20through%20their%20deliberate%20erasure%20of%20Hindu%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20witnessing%20the%20grandeur%20of%20development%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20days%20we%20will%20see%20the%20splendour%20of%20heritage.%20%3Cem%3EYahi%20toh%20Bharat%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(This%20is%20all%20India%20is%20all%20about)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20declared%2C%20fusing%20his%20messages%20of%20vikas%20and%20virasat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704022073000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31154445%2FGCmRH66WEAAejGQ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fweeks-before-ram-temple-inauguration-pm-modi-and-a-pr-blitzkrieg-visit-ayodhya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20three%20pillars%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20Hindutva%2C%20development%20and%20welfare%20%E2%80%93%20were%20covered%20in%20Modi's%20speeches%20and%20agenda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fweeks-before-ram-temple-inauguration-pm-modi-and-a-pr-blitzkrieg-visit-ayodhya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Punjab%20Turned%20Down%20Centre's%20Offer%20To%20Display%20Tableau%20At%20Red%20Fort%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20Punjab's%20tableau%20will%20not%20be%20showcased%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Brejected%20category%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20said%20the%20state's%20tableau%20that%20was%20not%20selected%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20will%20not%20be%20displayed%20at%20Bharat%20Parv%20in%20Red%20Fort%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20political%20row%20over%20Punjab's%20tableau%20not%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20had%20written%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20inviting%20them%20to%20display%20it%20during%20Bharat%20Parv%20from%20January%2023%20to%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20here%20today%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20great%20martyrs%20including%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Shaheed%20Rajguru%2C%20Shaheed%20Sukhdev%2C%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%2C%20Shaheed%20Udham%20Singh%2C%20Shaheed%20Kartar%20Singh%20Sarabha%2C%20Mai%20Bhago%2C%20Ghadri%20Baabe%20and%20others%20cannot%20be%20kept%20in%20rejected%20category.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20belittle%20their%20contribution%20and%20sacrifice%20of%20these%20heroes%20by%20not%20including%20their%20tableaus%20in%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade.%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%20said%20that%20this%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%20as%20it%20is%20the%20grave%20insult%20of%20these%20great%20patriots%20and%20national%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20state%20will%20not%20send%20its%20tableaux%20%26quot%3Bas%20the%20martyrs%20of%20the%20country%20don't%20need%20NOC%20of%20BJP%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20don't%20need%20support%20of%20the%20union%20government%20to%20showcase%20their%20heroes%20rather%20it%20is%20capable%20enough%20to%20pay%20tributes%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20is%20Mr%20Mann's%20latest%20strike%20in%20the%20tableau%20row.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20had%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20discriminating%20against%20Punjab%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20they%20have%20their%20way%2C%20they%20will%20take%20out%20the%20word%20'Punjab'%20from%20the%20national%20anthem%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Punjab%20BJP%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Mann%20of%20politicising%20the%20issue.%20He%20had%20claimed%20that%20Punjab's%20tableau%20was%20not%20shortlisted%20because%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bcrude%26quot%3B%20make.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20wanted%20photos%20of%20party%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Mr%20Mann%20on%20the%20tableau.%20This%20is%20not%20allowed%20as%20per%20protocol%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20tableau's%20rejection%2C