agram%2C%20Karan%20shared%20a%20new%20selfie%20with%20both%20actors.%20About%20Alia%2C%20KJo%20wrote%20in%20his%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20years%20wraps%20I%20felt%20like%20sharing%20this%20with%20all%20of%20you...I%20hadn't%20directed%20Alia%20since%202012%20and%20the%20day%20she%20walked%20onto%20set%20In%20her%20%40manishmalhotra05%20plus%20%40mickeycontractor%20plus%20%23flavian%20look%20I%20knew%20we%20had%20the%20Rani%20I%20had%20always%20envisaged%20....%20What%20followed%20was%20an%20actor%20I%20wasn't%20prepared%20for....%20And%20I%20can%20take%20zero%20credit%20...%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20Imtiaz%20ali%20for%20taking%20her%20on%20a%20highway%20of%20life%20and%20moulding%20her%20into%20the%20actor%20she%20finally%20became.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wrote%20that%20Alia's%20true%20launch%20as%20an%20artist%20will%20always%20be%20'Highway.'%20%26quot%3BSOTY%20is%20technically%20her%20launch%20but%20her%20true%20launch%20as%20an%20artist%20will%20always%20be%20highway...%20Alia%20is%20such%20a%20pride%20and%20pleasure%20on%20a%20film%20set....%20She%20had%20a%20ticking%20mind%20constantly%20questioning%20Rani%20and%20trying%20her%20best%20to%20make%20her%20strong%20and%20yet%20identifiable%20and%20likeable%20...%20again%20for%20that%20I%20take%20no%20credit%20that%20is%20her%20evolution%20as%20an%20artist!%20Was%20blessed%20to%20have%20her%20as%20Rani%20Chatterjee%20and%20I%20do%20hope%20her%20character%20keeps%20resonating%20....%20Love%20you%20%40aliaabhatt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurely%2C%20Alia%20has%20had%20a%20great%20year.%20%3Cem%3EDarlings%3C%2Fem%3E%2C'%20Alia%20Bhatt's%20web%20debut%2C%20earned%20her%20the%20Best%20Actor%20(female)%20award%20in%20the%20Filmfare%20OTT%20Awards.%20Alia%20wore%20a%20black%20body-hugging%20outfit%20inspired%20by%20a%20saree%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2069th%20National%20Film%20Awards%20ceremony%2C%20actress%20Alia%20Bhatt%20received