%20an%20emblematic%20venue%20of%20the%20life%20and%20activities%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20before%20it%20came%20to%20be%20propagated%20as%20the%20enclave%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20here%20that%20Bapu-Gandhi%20gave%20his%20call%20for%20the%20non-cooperation%20movement%20in%201920%2C%20where%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20crowned%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%201959%2C%20where%20she%20made%20her%20triumphant%20return%20with%20a%20public%20address%20in%201980%20at%20the%20time%20of%20%C2%A0the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Janata%20experiment%2C%20sweeping%20Vidharba%20in%20the%20elections%20thereafter%2C%20where%2C%20in%20resounding%20rebuff%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esanatan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ambedkar%20converted%20to%20the%20Buddhist%20faith%20in%201956%20along%20with%20some%20600%2C000%20compatriots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20devotees%20of%20the%20right-wing%20might%20know%20that%20of%20the%2018%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Nagpur%20constituency%20from%201952%20onwards%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2013%2C%20and%20of%20the%2011%20that%20happened%20there%20after%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%201980%2C%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20won%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20this%20episode%20of%20political%20reclamation%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20entirely%20ingenious%20and%20justified.%20That%20it%20was%20attended%20by%20some%20200%2C000%20Congress%20people%20must%20go%20down%20as%20especially%20significant%2C%20given%20the%20current%20%3Cem%3Ezeitgeist%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20everyday%20laced%20with%20stories%20of%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20another%20matter%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20must%20now%20rise%20to%20embrace%20a%20praxis%20in%20which%20it%20operates%20as%20first%20among%20equals%2C%20with%20a%20selfless%2C%20common%20objective%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%20came%20the%20proclamation%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20as%2C%20if%20you%20like%2C%20the%20long-awaited%20Hindu%20counter%20to%20Mecca%20and%20the%20Vatican.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20this%20event%20has%20had%20the%20full%20muscle%20and%20money%20of%20the%20state%20to%20prop%20it%2C%20what%20wonder%20that%20the%20media%20should%20have%20flashed%20it%20as%20unrelentingly%20continuous%20fare%20on%20television%2C%20no%20holds%20barred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20culmination%20of%20the%20politics%20here%20is%20the%20stunningly%20audacious%20call%20given%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20that%20the%20nation%20celebrate%20Diwali%20on%20January%2022%20of%20the%20new%20year%20when%20the%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20due%20to%20be%20consecrated%20and%20installed%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20it%20seem%20sacrilegious%20that%20Modi%20should%20have%20made%20bold%20to%20rearrange%20the%20hallowed%20sanatan%20calendar%20of%20holy%20days%20rather%20to%20suit%20the%20political%20purposes%20of%20the%20right-wing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emahant%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20town%20who%20might%20make%20bold%20to%20point%20out%20to%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20as%20yet%20non-denominational%20government%20that%20it%20is%20not%20for%20him%20to%20recast%20the%20time%20of%20day%20on%20the%20calendar%20when%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Ayodhya%20after%20his%2014%20years%20of%20exile%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20unchallenged%20seems%20now%20the%20sway%20of%20the%20Modi%20cult%20that%20the%20Bonapartist%20edict%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20some%20nine%20months%20before%20the%20sanatan%20calendar%20warrants%20it%20may%20come%20to%20be%20lapped%20up%20with%20fervour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThinking%20back%2C%20what%20church%20after%20all%20had%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20%C2%A0up%20to%20Henry%20VIII%2C%20when%20he%20sought%20sanction%20for%20the%20annulment%20of%20his%20marriage%20with%20Katherine%20of%20Aragon%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20our%20Tudor%20days%20are%20here.%20So%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20Diwali%20%C2%A0be%20celebrated%20nine%20months%20before%20it%20is%20due%20if%20doing%20so%20helps%20hasten%20our%20leap%20to%20global%20majesty%2C%20breaking%20more%20Guiness%20records%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tudors%20are%20indeed%20here%2C%20proclaiming%20a%20daringly%20imaginative%20new%20Indian%20greatness%20wherein%20the%20sacred%20is%20as%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20yield%20to%20the%20profane%20as%20the%20profane%20to%20the%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20there%20is%20that%20third%20axis%20of%20modern%20Indian%20political%20life%2C%20the%20socialists%2C%20who%20have%20unsurprisingly%2C%20even%20adroitly%2C%20decided%20to%20resurrect%20and%20celebrate%20the%20memory%20of%20that%20first%20north-Indian%20ideologue%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20legendary%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20of%20Bihar.%20Since%20many%20of%20the%20socialists%20and%20social%20justice%20champions%20are%20powerful%20in%20individual%20states%2C%20it%20is%20useful%20to%20also%20see%20them%20as%20Indian%20federalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECannily%2C%20this%20event%20will%20coincide%20with%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20idol%20in%20the%20new%20temple%2C%20offering%20thus%20both%20a%20discomforting%20reminder%20of%20the%20fault-lines%20that%20continue%20to%20bedevil%20the%20sanatan%2C%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20also%20of%20an%20alternate%20interpretation%20of%20the%20legacy%20of%20lord%20Ram%20%E2%80%93%20one%20in%20which%20he%20is%20best%20emulated%20as%20someone%20who%20renounced%20his%20claim%20to%20state%20power%20for%20a%20higher%20ethical%20ideal%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20so-called%20Ram%20bhaktas%20who%20think%20nothing%20of%20using%20Ram%20cynically%20to%20latch%20on%20to%20state%20power%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAltogether%2C%20a%20fascinating%20configuration%20is%20set%20to%20vie%20for%20the%20heartstrings%20of%20the%20people%20as%20the%20terminally%20significant%20general%20elections%20of%20April-May%202024%20draw%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20up%20to%20the%20citizen%20to%20take%20her%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20thereby%20may%20hang%20quite%20a%20devastating%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704017944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31154821%2FGCb6K6BXAAAQytY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-modi-decrees-a-new-diwali-remember-theres-more-to-indian-politics-than-bjps-ram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20three%20axes%20on%20which%20the%20election%20of%202024%20will%20turn%20%E2%80%93%20Hindutva%2C%20a%20re-energised%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20social%20justice%20agenda%20of%20the%20socialists-federalists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-modi-decrees-a-new-diwali-remember-theres-more-to-indian-politics-than-bjps-ram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heaviest%20snow%20in%20Seoul%20for%20more%20than%2040%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704017940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-goyang-south-korea_6408285.jpg%3F20231231102401%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fheaviest-snow-in-south-koreas-capital-seoul-for-more-than-40-years-13039985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seoul%20has%20seen%20its%20biggest%20single-day%20snowfall%20for%20more%20than%2040%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A289%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhe