ravery!%20%F0%9F%99%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRezangLa%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RezangLa%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKumaon%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Kumaon%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBraveSoldiers%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BraveSoldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUILzTeNYsi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FUILzTeNYsi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Konchok%20Stanzin%20(%40kstanzinladakh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkstanzinladakh%2Fstatus%2F1739317589204189268%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accompanying%20picture%20in%20the%20councillor%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20a%20raised%20plinth%20construction%20by%208%20Kumaon%20in%20October%202020%20which%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20site%2C%20Maj%20Shaitan%20Singh%2C%20PVC%20(P)%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20mortally%20wounded%20leading%20his%20brave%20men%20into%20battle.%E2%80%9D%20On%20the%20sidearms%20of%20the%20raised%20plinths%20are%20etched%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20memory%20of%20the%20brave%20soldiers%20of%20C%20Coy%2C%2013%20Kumaon%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CMay%20their%20souls%20rest%20in%20peace%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2029%2C%20a%20question%20was%20posed%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%2C%20Arindam%20Bagchi%2C%20during%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37488%2FTranscript_of_Weekly_Media_Briefing_by_the_Official_Spokesperson_December_29_2023%5C%22%3Eweekly%20press%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20question%20by%20Sandeep%20from%20%3Cem%3ENews18%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20many%20of%20you%20know%2C%20there%20is%20a%20longstanding%20memorial%20to%20the%20Heroes%20of%20Rezang%20La%2C%20on%20the%20border.%20Any%20imputation%20that%20there%20has%20been%20any%20change%20in%20that%20monument%20is%20incorrect.%20And%20for%20any%20details%2C%20I%20would%20refer%20you%20to%20the%20concerned%20authorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioned%20further%20by%20Snehesh%20Alex%20Philip%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CSandeep%20was%20referring%20to%20was%20Shaitan%20Singh%20Memorial%2C%20which%20is%20there%20has%20that%20been%20dismantled%20or%20not.%20The%20Rezang%20La%20Memorial%2C%20of%20course%20remains%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20the%20Rezang%20La%20Memorial%20stands%20there.%20On%20the%20other%20one%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20information.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20for%20any%20details%20of%20that%20one%2C%20you%20would%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20concerned%20authorities%2C%20but%20the%20one%20which%20is%20longstanding%20and%20well%20known%20is%20the%20Rezang%20La%20Memorial.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concerned%20authorities%20are%20the%20army%20and%20the%20defence%20ministry%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20maintained%20silence%20on%20the%20matter.%20Army%20PRO%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Sudhir%20Chamoli%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fhindi%2Farticles%2Fcd1d06vk4ydo%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20no%20information%20about%20the%20matter%20and%20he%20could%20not%20comment%20on%20it%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Ladakh%20Jamyang%20Tshering%20Namgyal%20told%20the%20BBC%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20removal%20of%20the%20old%20memorial%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20one%20is%20not%20related%20to%20any%20kind%20of%20buffer%20zone.%20Has%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20said%20that%20a%20buffer%20zone%20has%20been%20created%3F%20We%20have%20built%20a%20big%20memorial%20for%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%20and%20it%20is%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20sacrifice.%20Those%20who%20are%20saying%20that%20that%20area%20has%20been%20made%20a%20no-man%E2%80%99s%20land%20are%20not%20telling%20the%20truth.%20The%20population%20of%20Chushul%20is%20living%20there%20and%20the%20roads%20there%20are%20also%20the%20same.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20there%20was%20some%20problem%20for%20the%20people%20around%20because%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20used%20to%20come%20and%20pay%20obeisance%20at%20the%20martyr%E2%80%99s%20site%20and%20there%20was%20tourism.%20But%20the%20memorial%20of%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%20and%20his%20sacrifice%20have%20not%20been%20diminished%20in%20any%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statements%20of%20Namgyal%20and%20Bagchi%20point%20to%20a%20deliberate%20misdirection%20of%20the%20construction%20at%20Rzeang%20La%20with%20the%20memorial%20at%20Chushul%2027%20km%20away%20from%20the%20site.%20The%20Chushul%20memorial%20was%20erected%20at%20the%20cremation%20place%20of%2096%20soldiers%20of%2013%20Kumaon%20in%20Chushul%20High%20Ground%20and%20inaugurated%20on%20August%205%2C%201963.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%201962%20war%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20was%20not%20deployed%20at%20Rezang%20la.%20It%20constructed%20the%20memorial%20at%20Chushul%20to%20mark%20the%20battle%20fought%20on%20November%2018%2C%201962.%20Out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20127%20all%20ranks%2C%20one%20officer%2C%20two%20JCOs%2C%20and%20105%20other%20ranks%20fell%20in%20battle%3B%20one%20JCO%20and%20four%20other%20ranks%20were%20taken%20prisoner%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20them%20later%20succumbed%20to%20his%20wounds.%20Only%20four%20soldiers%20returned%20alive.%20Two%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-archive%2Fweb%2Fnobody-believed-we-had-killed-so-many-chinese-at-rezang-la-our-commander-called-me-crazy-and-warned-that-i-could-be-courtmartialled%2F%5C%22%3Espoke%20about%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%201963%2C%20an%20Indian%20Army%20patrol%20reached%20Rezang%20La%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiasentinels.com%2Fopinion%2Fwe-stared-in-the-eyes-of-death-the-1962-operations-in-chushul-5871%5C%22%3Ediscovered%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20body%20near%20where%20he%20was%20last%20seen%20by%20his%20two%20men%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20official%20Indian%20history%20of%20the%20war%20records%20that%20his%20well-preserved%20body%20due%20to%20freezing%20temperatures%20showed%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20had%20received%20eight%20bullets%20and%20was%20still%20clutching%20his%20gun%E2%80%9D.%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20mortal%20remains%20were%20flown%20to%20Jodhpur%20on%20February%2019%2C%201963.%20Subsequently%2C%20Brigadier%20T.N.%20Raina%2C%20Commander%20of%20114%20Brigade%20personally%20went%20to%20Rezang%20la%20with%20a%20large%20party%20to%20collect%20the%20dead.%20Rezang%20la%20had%2096%20bodies%20which%20were%20cremated%20at%20Chushul%2C%20at%20a%20site%20which%20the%20battalion%20headquarters%20of%2013%20Kumaon%20during%20the%201962%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20structure%20that%20has%20been%20dismantled%20in%20February%202021%20was%20the%20site%20near%20Rezang%20la%20where%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20discovered%20in%201963%2C%20months%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dismantling%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20disengagement%20plan%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20Chinese%20PLA.%20This%20was%20announced%20by%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20in%20Parliament%20in%20February%202021%2C%20but%20no%20details%20of%20the%20buffer%20zone%20were%20provided.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-china-ladakh%5C%22%3EReports%3C%2Fa%3E%20state%20that%20under%20the%20plan%2C%20both%20sides%20would%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Kailash%20range%20(which%20India%20had%20moved%20into%20in%20August%202020)%20and%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20the%20Pangong%20Lake%20(where%20the%20PLA%20had%20entered%20in%20April%202020).%20A%20no-patrol%20zone%20would%20be%20created%20on%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20Pangong%20in%20the%20contested%20area%2C%20and%20the%20PLA%20would%20dismantle%20all%20the%20infrastructure%20it%20created%20there.%20It%20would%20also%20erase%20the%20Chinese%20map%2C%20flag%20and%20the%20slogan%20painted%20there%20earlier.%20There%20was%20great%20disappointment%20among%20observers%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20barter%20away%20its%20trump%20card%20in%20Kailash%20for%20only%20the%20north%20bank%20of%20Pangong%2C%20instead%20of%20seeking%20disengagement%20throughout%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20senior%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-china-ladakh%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20north%20bank%20was%20a%20priority%20for%20us%20because%20of%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20national%20morale%2C%20as%20the%20PLA%20had%20painted%20the%20China%20map%20and%20flag.%20We%20wanted%20to%20get%20that%20removed.%E2%80%9D%20The%20landmark%20at%20Rezang%20la%20constructed%20in%20October%202020%20was%20dismantled%20as%20part%20of%20that%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2023%2F01%2Findia-has-lost-access-to-26-of-65-patrolling-points-in-ladakh-says-research-paper%2F%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%20presented%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20annual%20conference%20of%20police%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20January%2C%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20senior%20superintendent%20of%20police%20P.D.%20Nithya%20said%20India%20had%20lost%20access%20to%2026%20of%2065%20patrolling%20points%20in%20Ladakh%20from%20the%20Karakoram%20Pass%20to%20Chumar%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20since%202020.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20%E2%80%9Ctowards%20the%20Indian%20side%E2%80%9D%2C%20