itoon%20nani%2C%20the%20oldest%20member%20of%20the%20staff%2C%20was%20also%20there%2C%20resting%20on%20her%20small%20chowki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmma!%20What%E2%80%99s%20for%20dinner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20only%20six.%20You%20want%20dinner%20now!%20I%20have%20to%20first%20cook%20dinner%20for%20the%20table.%20Why%20do%20you%20want%20dinner%20now%3F%20You%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20been%20out%20on%20your%20evening%20jaunt%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20way%20he%20was%20dressed%2C%20in%20tight%2C%20tapered%20pants%20and%20an%20equally%20tight-fitting%20jacket%2C%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20he%20was%20intending%20to%20go%20out%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20want%20dinner.%20Salman%20scowled%20at%20her%20and%20turned%20to%20leave.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20eat%20out%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20were%20you%20asking%20me%3F%20Anyway%20you%20eat%20out%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%2C%20sometimes%20at%20that%20witch%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%20How%20she%20has%20done%20black%20magic%20on%20you!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaitoon%20nani%20clucked%20her%20tongue.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20very%20bad%20influence%2C%20Sallu.%20You%20are%20wasting%20your%20time%20instead%20of%20finding%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinding%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20scoffed.%20%E2%80%9CNani%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20ask%20Badey%20saheb%20to%20get%20me%20some%20decent%20work%3F%20I%20promise%20I%E2%80%99ll%20leave%20everything%20and%20focus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20he%20find%20you%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20big%20man.%20He%20knows%20everybody.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20is%3A%20in%20our%20community%2C%20important%20people%20turn%20their%20faces%20away%20from%20people%20like%20me.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20our%20eyes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20embarrassment%2C%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%2C%20so%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20looking%3F%E2%80%9D%20At%20times%20Zaitoon%20nani%20could%20be%20very%20perceptive%20about%20her%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%20at%20Bulbhaddar%20babu%3A%20he%20has%20helped%20Shambhu%20and%20those%20two%20thugs%2C%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20There%20is%20nobody%20to%20help%20us.%20Amma%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20at%20least%20send%20me%20to%20a%20proper%20school%3F%20She%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20madarsa%20to%20save%20money.%20Now%20I%20am%20stuck.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%2010th%C2%A0class%20certificate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20night%20and%20day%20to%20feed%20you.%20Where%20was%20the%20money%20to%20send%20you%20to%20an%20English%20school%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeta%2C%20even%20if%20you%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20most%20famous%20English%20school%2C%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20had%20any%20papers%20to%20show.%20You%20get%20a%20degree%20if%20you%20properly%20pass%20your%20exams.%20When%20you%20keep%20running%20away%20from%20school%2C%20then%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20English%20school%20or%20an%20Arabi%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zaitoon%20nani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20shrugged%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20birth%20certificate%2C%20or%20any%20other%20certificate.%20When%20they%20come%20with%20the%20NRC%20register%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%3F%20Fine!%20Let%20them%20put%20my%20name%20on%20the%20register%20and%20deport%20me.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care.%20My%20Amma%20and%20my%20nani%20will%20have%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%20He%20banged%20the%20wooden%20courtyard%20door%20as%20he%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20he%20suddenly%20want%20papers%3F%E2%80%9D%20his%20mother%20asked%2C%20looking%20towards%20Zaitoon%20nani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArshad%20bhai%2C%20plea