big%20margin%2C%20causing%20a%20public%20meltdown%20among%20many%20of%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers.%20Even%20then%2C%20the%20newly-elected%20Sanjay%20Singh%20made%20no%20bones%20about%20his%20close%20association%20with%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20and%20announced%20that%20the%20junior%20national%20tournaments%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Nandini%20Nagar%20in%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20stronghold%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gonda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20BJP%20MP%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20play%20a%20key%20campaigning%20role%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20suspended%20the%20newly-elected%20leadership%20of%20the%20WFI%20for%20alleged%20irregularities%2C%20and%20replaced%20it%20with%20a%20three-member%20ad-hoc%20committee%20soon%20after%20Olympian%20Sakshi%20Malik%20announced%20her%20retirement%20as%20yet%20another%20mark%20of%20protest.%20With%20Phogat%20now%20returning%20her%20awards%2C%20the%20matter%20refuses%20to%20end%20even%20as%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20continues%20to%20remain%20in%20a%20limbo.%20Earlier%2C%20Punia%20too%20had%20returned%20his%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Phogat%20kept%20her%20awards%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Kartavya%20Path.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20picked%20the%20medals%20later.%20Earlier%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Modi%2C%20Phogat%20has%20claimed%20that%20women%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20lives%20are%20not%20like%20those%20%E2%80%9Cfancy%20government%20advertisements%E2%80%9D%20that%20talk%20about%20women%E2%80%99s%20upliftment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Punia%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20wrestling%20activities%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20as%20there%20have%20been%20no%20tournaments%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20in%207%20months%20but%20no%20one%20seems%20serious%20about%20it%20while%20in%20the%20last%20four%20Olympics%2C%20wrestlers%20brought%20consecutive%20medals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punia%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704005072000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120945%2FScreenshot-2023-12-31-at-12.09.08-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20said%20that%20such%20awards%20were%20meaningless%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20Dark%20Year%2C%20Films%20and%20Series%20That%20Spoke%20of%20Idealism%2C%20Courage%20and%20Hope%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120511%2FHM-films.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20that%20we%20leave%20behind%20was%20a%20sombre%2C%20troubled%20one%20both%20for%20India%20and%20for%20much%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20politics%20of%20hate%20engulfed%20more%20and%20more%20people.%20Bombs%20pitilessly%20pounded%20children%20and%20hospitals%20in%20Gaza%20on%20a%20scale%20not%20seen%20this%20century%2C%20civilians%20picked%20up%20firearms%20against%20each%20other%20converting%20Manipur%20into%20an%20implacable%20war%20zone%2C%20and%20lynchings%20continued%20in%20India%2C%20barely%20noticed%20any%20more.%20Democracy%20faltered%2C%20inequality%20further%20soared%20and%20India%20fell%20even%20further%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fitting%2C%20then%2C%20that%20the%20marker%20of%20the%20worthiest%20of%20Hindi%20films%20and%20shows%20of%202023%20was%20a%20common%20strain%20of%20dogged%20humanism%20%E2%80%93%20of%20idealism%2C%20courage%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20they%20acknowledged%20the%20crises%20of%20inequality%2C%20injustice%20and%20hate%20that%20cobble%20the%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20that%20six%20of%20the%20nine%20films%20and%20shows%20listed%20here%20are%20based%20on%20true-life%20stories.%20And%20even%20those%20that%20are%20fictional%20are%20close%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20front%20line%20among%20my%20favourite%20films%20was%20one%20that%20came%20early%20in%20the%20year%2C%20Nandita%20Das%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EZwigato%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20narrative%20of%20aching%20tenderness%20and%20gentle%20rage.%20Das%20carefully%20observes%20the%20quiet%20struggles%2C%20the%20dignity%2C%20the%20resolve%2C%20the%20hurt%20and%20the%20determined%20love%20of%20Manas%20Mahto%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20food%20delivery%20man%2C%20and%20Pratima%20who%20steps%20out%20warily%20to%20share%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20burdens%2C%20as%20a%20masseuse%20to%20rich%20women%20in%20high-rise%20apartments%20and%20as%20a%20janitor%20in%20a%20mall.%20With%20luminous%20empathy%2C%20Kapil%20Sharma%20and%20Shahana%20Goswami%20portray%20how%20both%20try%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20other%20from%20the%20humiliations%2C%20the%20insults%20and%20disappointments%20that%20they%20endure%20as%20they%20daily%20grapple%20with%20the%20uncaring%2C%20unequal%20world%20of%20rich%20and%20middle-class%20India.%20Their%20unostentatious%20but%20steadfast%20love%20for%20each%20other%20and%20for%20those%20in%20their%20care%20forms%20the%20moral%20core%20of%20the%20film%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%20its%20only%20fount%20of%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18.jpeg%5C%22%2