Meghwal.%20As%20Bhaati%2C%20her%20caste%20identity%20was%20ambiguous.%20As%20Meghwal%2C%20she%20is%20unmistakably%2C%20defiantly%20and%20proudly%20Dalit.%20%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Wire%20Recommends%3A%20Eight%20Movies%20We%20Watched%20and%20Liked%20This%20Year%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-wire-recommends-movies%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%20Recommends%3A%20Eight%20Movies%20We%20Watched%20and%20Liked%20This%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20Dalit%20identity%20of%20another%20police%20officer%20that%20raises%20%3Cem%3EBheed%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20searing%20documentation%20of%20the%20great%20migrant%20exodus%20that%20erupted%20after%20the%20Indian%20government%20imposed%20with%20four-hours%E2%80%99%20notice%20a%20punishing%20nation-wide%20lockdown.%20The%20police%20officer%20hides%20his%20Dalit%20identity%20with%20his%20upper-caste%20surname%2C%20Surya%20Kumar%20Singh.%20But%20his%20superior%20officer%20never%20fails%20to%20remind%20him%20of%20his%20caste.%20Singh%20is%20charged%20with%20blocking%20the%20movement%20of%20a%20crowd%20of%20migrants%20at%20a%20rural%20roadblock%20erected%20to%20prevent%20hundreds%20of%20starving%20workers%20desperate%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages.%20The%20film%E2%80%99s%20director%20Anubhav%20Sinha%20deploys%20the%20range%20of%20characters%20heaving%20at%20the%20roadblock%20to%20depict%20how%20the%20fractures%20of%20class%2C%20caste%20and%20religious%20identity%20collapsed%20solidarities%20in%20this%20time%20of%20monumental%20disaster%20when%20people%20most%20needed%20to%20stand%20together.%20I%20bore%20first-hand%20witness%20to%20this%2C%20the%20greatest%20humanitarian%20crisis%20since%20Partition%2C%20and%20feel%20that%20Sinha%20falls%20short%20in%20reflecting%20the%20depth%20and%20range%20of%20the%20tragedy%20and%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20culpability%20of%20the