e%20located%20five%20km%20apart.%20The%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20a%20Meitei%20man%2C%20Ningombam%2C%20who%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%20from%20a%20bomb%20blast%20in%20Kadanban%20village.%20A%20press%20note%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20also%20confirmed%20the%20death%20of%20the%20civilian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20another%20gunfight%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20began%20in%20the%20evening%20in%20Moreh%20district%2C%20where%20a%20police%20officer%20was%20injured.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20(AR)%20were%20attempting%20to%20control%20the%20situation%20in%20Moreh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20142%20nakas%20(checkpoints)%20were%20installed%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20Manipur%2C%20both%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%2C%20where%20the%20police%20detained%20204%20persons%20in%20connection%20with%20violations%20in%20various%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20search%20operation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Manipur%20Police%20also%20recovered%20different%20types%20of%20weapons%2C%20including%20hand%20grenades%2C%20cartridges%2C%20stun%20grenades%2C%20ammunition%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20more%20than%20200%20people%20have%20died%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20began.%20This%20data%20also%20includes%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20that%20have%20occurred%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703997271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31100356%2FGCm-A9Pa4AAS-Sn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-another-person-killed-as-ethnic-violence-continues%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deceased%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20James%20Ningombam%20from%20Mayang-langjing%20in%20the%20Imphal%20West%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%