%3E%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejournalists%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emedical%20personnel%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Gaza.%20It%20was%20a%20year%20when%20the%20world%20threw%20its%20weighty%20tome%20of%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Humanitarian%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20under%20an%20%3Cem%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%3C%2Fem%3E%20(IDF)%20tank.%20This%20war%20was%20far%20more%20brutal%20than%20anything%20the%20present%20century%20had%20seen%20and%20possibly%20anything%20witnessed%20during%2020th%20century%2C%20with%20its%20legacy%20stained%20by%20the%20poppy%20fields%20of%20Flanders%20and%20the%20rice%20paddies%20of%20Vietnam%3B%20the%20aerial%20bombardments%20of%20Dresden%20and%20the%20Balkan%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Cem%3EOctober%207%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EHamas%3C%2Fem%3E%20invaded%20Israel%20and%20killed%201%2C200%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20tons%20of%20explosives%20have%20been%20dropped%20by%20the%20IDF%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EGaza%20Strip%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20the%20two%20nuclear%20bombs.%20It%20left%20whole%20neighbourhoods%20reduced%20to%20%3Cem%3Erubble%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20a%20death%20toll%20of%20over%2020%2C000%20and%20mounting.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20feeling%20that%20this%20was%20some%20simulated%20%3Cem%3EAI%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecreation.%20But%20the%20blood%20was%20real%20and%20splattered%20on%20our%20skin%3B%20the%20debris%20from%20blown-up%20hospitals%20settled%20in%20our%20lungs%20even%20as%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%93%20a%20legacy%20from%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20continued%20to%20smolder%20under%20Russian%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20year%20when%20India%20overtook%20China%20to%20become%20the%20globe%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Emost%20populous%3C%2Fem%3E%20country.%20Even%20as%20the%20world%20teetered%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20climate%20catastrophe%2C%20it%20tried%20to%20negotiate%20a%20climate%20deal%20at%20%3Cem%3ECOP28%20%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20cop-out%20eventually%2C%20with%20some%20clever%20language%20on%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%20away%20from%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20rather%20than%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cphasing%20out%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20fossil%20fuels%20making%20it%20to%20the%20final%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBigotry%20and%20hate%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20abloom%20in%202023.%20Ethnic%20polarization%20%3Cem%3Ein%20Manipur%3C%2Fem%3E%20set%20off%20Hill%20against%20Valley%2C%20%3Cem%3EKuki-Zo%3C%2Fem%3E%20against%20%3Cem%3EMeitei%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20conflagration%20that%20resulted%20in%20brutal%20killings%20and%20widespread%20displacement%20of%20people%20raged%20for%20months.%20Its%20bestiality%20came%20home%20to%20every%20Indian%20when%20a%20%3Cem%3Evideo%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20then%20gang%20raped%2C%20went%20viral%20in%20July%2C%20weeks%20after%20the%20actual%20incident.%20The%20video%20squeezed%20a%20few%20reluctant%20words%20out%20of%20our%20political%20leadership%20who%20had%20thus%20far%20watched%20the%20state%20burn%20silently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBigotry%20saw%3Cem%3E%20churches%3C%2Fem%3E%20burned%20in%20%3Cem%3EManipur%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20temple%20attacked%20in%20%3Cem%3ENuh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emosques%3C%2Fem%3E%20threatened%20with%20demolition%20across%20India%20that%20is%20%3Cem%3EBharat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Bharat%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20doppelganger%20came%20alive%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3EPresident%20of%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E%20invited%20dignitaries%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EG20%3C%2Fem%3E%20do.%20Speaking%20of%20G20%2C%20its%20events%20crowded%20the%20year%2C%20throwing%20out%20street%20vendors%20and%20curtaining%20away%20slums.%20Over%20a%20thousand%20promotional%20G20%20posters%20beamed%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20walls%20during%20the%20main%20event%2C%20a%20quarter%20of%20which%20bore%20the%20smiling%20visage%20of%20the%20PM.%20They%20provoked%20comments%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EGeneral%20Election%3C%2Fem%3E%20seemed%20to%20have%20come%20a%20tad%20too%20early.%20But%20elections%20were%20never%20far%20from%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20who%20slipped%20effortlessly%2C%20every%20now%20and%20then%2C%20into%20election%20mode%2C%20allowing%20himself%20to%20be%20bathed%20in%20marigolds%20flung%20by%20well-choreographed%20adoring%20crowds.%20These%20scenes%20presumably%20were%20just%20trailers%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3E2024%20%3C%2Fem%3Eblockbuster%20which%20the%20BJP%20claims%20it%20has%20already%20won%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20%3Cem%3EINDIA%3C%2Fem%3E%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fem%3E%20finally%20settled%20the%20question%20looming%20over%20India%20since%202019%20and%20which%20had%20tortured%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20all%20these%20years%3A%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Eabrogation%20of%20Article%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%20legal%3F%20The%20five-judge%20bench%20had%20no%20problem%20in%20arriving%20at%20the%20conclusion%3A%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20was.%20One%20judge%20asked%20for%20a%20process%20of%20%3Cem%3Etruth%20and%20reconciliation%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20region.%20What%20truth%3F%20What%20reconciliation%3F%20The%20torture%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebakarwals%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20army%20reinforced%20the%20truth%20that%20this%20wound%20has%20no%20healing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20year%20when%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20was%20officially%20designated%20a%20Government%20of%20India-owned%20enterprise%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20portentously%20named%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20law%20which%20allows%20the%20PM%20and%20a%20minister%20of%20his%20choosing%20to%20be%20two%20of%20three%20members%20constituting%20the%20selection%20committee%20for%20the%20three%20election%20commissioners.%20Will%20this%20impact%20future%20elections%20in%20Bharat%3F%20Time%20will%20tell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fate%20of%20the%20ECI%20seemed%20to%20reflect%20the%20general%20meltdown%20of%20institutions.%20When%20caged%20parrots%20roar%20lion-like%20and%20courts%20adopt%20a%20%3Cem%3Etareekh%20pe%20tareekh%3C%2Fem%3E%20regimen%2C%20endlessly%20sitting%20on%20momentous%20cases%2C%20endlessly%20postponing%20the%20possibility%20of%20bail%20for%20our%20prisoners%20of%20conscience%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20in%20a%20system%20of%20checks%20and%20balances%2C%20the%20balances%20have%20been%20checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20institution%20that%20perhaps%20suffered%20the%20greatest%20in%20this%20year%20of%20meltdowns%20was%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%2C%20now%20housed%20in%20a%20grand%20new%20building%20that%20reminded%20onlookers%20of%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station.%20The%20royal%20%3Cem%3Esengol%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sceptre)%20installed%20above%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20Chair%20did%20nothing%20to%20remind%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20their%20kartavya%20(duties)%20during%20an%20era%20designated%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekartavya%20kaal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20farcical%20nature%20of%20the%20disqualification%20of%20%3Cem%3EMahua%20Moitra%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20no%20less%20than%20150%20Opposition%20members%20were%20expelled%20from%20the%20House%20for%20nothing%20more%20than%20demanding%20accountability%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20a%20serious%20%3Cem%3Ebreach%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Parliament%2C%20marked%20a%20new%20low.%20Bills%20that%20could%20have%20deleterious%20consequences%20were%20passed%20with%20lightning%20speed%2C%20often%20in%20the%20total%20absence%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20bills%20shrinking%20the%20democratic%20and%20media%20space%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%2C%20prisoners%20of%20conscience%20like%20Bhima%20Koregaon%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EShoma%20Sen%3C%2Fem%3E%20marked%20five%20years%20behind%20bars.%20Meanwhile%20the%20coercive%20agencies%20were%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20more%20candidates%20deserving%20state%20hospitality.%20The%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20got%20raided%20for%20daring%20to%20put%20footage%20from%20the%202002%20era%2C%20and%20journalists%20and%20associates%20of%20the%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20confronted%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel%20at%20dawn%2C%20with%20its%20septuagenarian%20founder-editor%20being%20promptly%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPenal%20laws%20got%20a%20facelift%20this%20year.%20The%20%3Cem%3EBharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EBharatiya%20Sakshya%20Act%3C%2Fem%3E%20replaced%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20and%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20respectively.%20Yet%2C%20despite%20their%20weighty%20nomenclatures%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20feeling%20that%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%20was%20in%20subsidence%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sinking%20feeling%20found%20a%20parallel%20in%20the%20geographical%20space.%20Early%20in%202023%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20temple%20town%20of%20%3Cem%3EJoshimath%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20rendered%20uninhabitable%20because%20it%20had%20caved%20in.%20Questions%20as%20to%20what%20caused%20this%20disaster%20were%20never%20allowed%20to%20fully%20surface%20but%20nature%20persists%20in%20its%20search%20for%20answers.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ESilkyara%20tunnel%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20those%20that%20were%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ci%3EChar%20Dham%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0road%20widening%20project%2C%20collapsed%2C%20trapping%20%3Cem%3E41%3C%2Fem%3E%20workers.%20It%20took%2017%20days%20and%20the%20expert%20skills%20of%20%3Cem%3Erat%20hole%20miners%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20finally%20%3Cem%3Erescue%3C%2Fem%3E%20them.%20Did%20India%20need%20this%20road%20widening%20project%20that%20involves%20cutting%20into%20fragile%20Himalayan%20hill%20sides%3F%C2%A0%20Well%2C%20the%20machines%20at%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20have%20renewed%20their%20drilling%2C%20how%E2%80%99%20that%20for%20an%20answer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20year%20that%20saw%20a%20slew%20of%20%3Cem%3EVande%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E%20trains%20criss-cross%20the%20country%2C%20often%20flagged%20off%20for%20their%20inaugural%20run%20by%20the%20PM%20himself.%20Before%20long%2C%20we%20got%20the%20%3Cem%3ENamo%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E%20bearing%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20name%20which%20was%20once%20again%20enthusiastically%20flagged%20off%20by%20him.%20But%20these%20shiny%20new%20things%20were%20not%20for%20the%20plebs.%20They%20had%20to%20make%20do%20with%20the%20old%20iron%20horses%20that%20form%20the%20core%20of%20railway%20operations%2C%20often%20jumping%20through%20the%20windows%20to%20get%20standing%20room.%20Nothing%20reflected%20the%20great%20divide%20in%20rail%20travel%20than%20the%20tragic%20accident%20in%20%3Cem%3EBalasore%3C%2Fem%3E%20involving%20three%20trains%20and%20claiming%20288%20lives.%20What%20caused%20the%20tragedy%3F%20Signal%20breakdown%3F%20Human%20error%3F%20Failure%20to%20follow%20safety%20norms%3F%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20politicize%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20the%20Union%20Railways%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOkay%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20content%20ourselves%20instead%20with%20clapping%20as%20yet%20another%20Namo%20Bharat%20gets%20inaugurated%20and%20waving%20the%20flag%20as%20%3Cem%3EChandrayan-3%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20a%20historic%20moon%20landing.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20excise%20the%20%3Cem%3EMughals%3C%2Fem%3E%20so%20thoroughly%20from%20our%20consciousness%20that%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20famed%20Mughal%20Gardens%20became%20%3Cem%3EAmrit%20Udayan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20confine%20%3Cem%3EDarwin%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20the%20dustbin%20for%20daring%20to%20suggest%20that%20we%20descend%20from%20apes.%20As%20for%20eggs%20in%20midday%20meals%2C%20why%20do%20we%20need%20them%20when%20we%20have%20potatoes%20that%20look%20so%20similar%3F%C2%A0%20And%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20of%20romancing%20anybody%20on%20Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekissing%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewill%20be%20restricted%20to%3Cem%3E%20cows%20%3C%2Fem%3Eonly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFull%20marks%20however%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Ewomen%20wrestlers%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20took%20on%20a%20political%20heavyweight%20and%20sexual%20predator%20without%20flinching%2C%20pinning%20him%20down%20in%20their%20lock%20and%20hold.%20This%20meant%20sitting%20out%20in%20%3Cem%3EJantar%20Mantar%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20weeks%20on%20end%2C%20it%20also%20meant%20the%20ultimate%20sacrifice%20of%20ending%20a%20career%20for%20one%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ESakshi%20Malik%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewho%20deserves%20a%20gold%20for%20that%20supreme%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F03090519%2FFu-TI4nagAA3RYL.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F03090519%2FFu-TI4nagAA3RYL.jpeg%20739w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F03090519%2FFu-TI4nagAA3RYL-300x168.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22415%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E(L-R)%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40RakeshTikaitBKU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20had%20its%20share%20of%20eccentrics%2C%20with%20%3Cem%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fem%3E%20leading%20the%20pack.%20It%20was%20not%20just%20that%20he%20crossed%20out%20Twitter%20with%20an%20enormous%20%3Cem%3EX%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3Ebye%20bye%20bluebird%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20he%20was%20also%20fixated%20on%20his%20Neuralink%20programme%3A%20an%20implantable%20%3Cem%3EBrain%20Computer%20Interface%20(BCI).%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20year%20he%20received%20approval%20to%20take%20the%20initial%20steps%20towards%20what%20could%20be%20the%20first%20human%20trial%20of%20BCI%20in%20paralysis%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20our%20own%20BCCI%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20a%20%3Cem%3Enepo%20baby%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20made%20news%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20premier%20money%20making%20cricket%20body%2C%20by%20earning%20%246.02%20billion%20through%20selling%20media%20rights%20to%20cover%20IPL%20in%20the%20period%20between%202023-2027.%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20last%20big%20tourney%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20the%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20brought%20in%20a%20record-breaking%201%2C250%2C307%20spectators.%20Most%20of%20them%20left%20before%20the%20final%20ceremony%20because%20their%20team%20had%20failed%20to%20lift%20the%20cup%2C%20which%20shows%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20cricket%20lover%20and%20a%20nationalist%20bigot%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20no%20prophet%20and%20this%20is%20no%20%3Cem%3EProphet%20Song%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20as%20we%20leap%20blindly%20into%20a%20%3Cem%3Eleap%20year%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20let%20courage%20and%20humour%20be%20our%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrong%20call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2024%2C%20podcaster%20Ravi%20Handa%20called%20out%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20tweet%20for%20featuring%20Suhel%20Seth%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20had%20introduced%20him%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwell-known%20and%20highly%20regarded%20individual%E2%80%9D.%20Handa%20recalled%20that%20this%20portal%20had%20carried%20a%20piece%20in%202019%20which%20had%20referenced%20the%20accusations%20against%20Seth%20for%20sexual%20harassment.%20His%20tweet%20went%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202023%3A%20Suhel%20Seth%20is%20a%20well-known%20and%20highly%20regarded%20individual.%20The%20Wire%20in%202019%3A%20Suhel%20Seth%20is%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20several%20women.%20U-turn%20took%204%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20NWMIndia%2C%20a%20collective%20that%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20speaking%20out%20on%20journalistic%20norms%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20gender%2C%20put%20out%20a%20tweet%20addressed%20to%20%40thewire_in%20and%20%40KaranThapar_TTP%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98all%20those%20involved%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20you%20normalize%20and%20celebrate%20a%20man%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20harassment%20and%20molestation%20by%20multiple%20women%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20another%20of%20its%20tweets%20pointing%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cchampioning%20liberal%20values%20and%20support%20a%20%23MeToo%20boys%E2%80%99club%20cannot%20go%20hand%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reader%2C%20N.%20Jayaram%2C%20mailed%20in%3A%20%E2%80%9CBewildered%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20response%C2%A0(unless%20mistaken)%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20(he%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20NWMI%20tweet).%C2%A0%20What%20do%20you%20make%20of%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20response%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Well%2C%20this%20was%20certainly%20a%20cringe-worthy%20moment%20for%20this%20portal%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Sakshi%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference%20and%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharma%20were%20big%20news%20points.%C2%A0%20An%20alert%20desk%20should%20have%20red-flagged%20the%20Seth%20interview%20before%20it%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day.%C2%A0%20By%20the%20time%20it%20was%20taken%20down%20it%20was%20too%20late%20because%20material%20on%20the%20internet%20has%20more%20lives%20than%20a%20feline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20old%20lesson%20for%20the%20new%20year%3F%20I%20hope%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsraelis%20not%20villains%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWire%20reader%20Tarakant%20Sinha%20responds%20to%20an%20exchange%20in%20the%20letters%20column%20of%20December%209%20between%20another%20reader%20and%20me%20(%E2%80%98Does%20Israel%20have%20a%20choice%3F%E2%80%99)%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CAcquisition%20of%20land%20by%20purchase%20in%20then%20Palestine%20started%20from%20late%2019th%20century%20and%20continued%20even%20after%20creation%20of%20Israel.%20The%20Israelis%20worked%20hard%20on%20the%20fallow%20land%20to%20make%20it%20bloom.%C2%A0%20All%20three%20wars%20%E2%80%94%201948%2C%201967%20and%20Yom%20Kippur1973%20were%20started%20by%20Arabs.%C2%A0%20So%20calling%20the%20Israelis%20villains%20from%20the%20beginning%20is%20unfair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20response%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20What%20about%20the%20British%20colonialists%20and%20their%20nefarious%20resettlement%20plan%3F%20The%20Balfour%20Declaration%20dates%20back%20to%201917%2C%20so%20clearly%20not%20all%20the%20land%20was%20commercially%20acquired%2C%20even%20if%20we%20are%20to%20give%20recognition%20to%20the%20land%20deals%20of%20a%20century%20and%20more%20ago.%C2%A0%20As%20for%20making%20the%20land%20%E2%80%9Cbloom%E2%80%9D%2C%20this%20was%20achieved%20largely%20through%20Palestinian%20labour.%20Palestinians%20had%20made%20their%20land%20bloom%20for%20centuries%20as%20testified%20by%20their%20legacy%20Olive%20trees.%20Palestine%2C%20incidentally%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20relatively%20more%20developed%20and%20industrial%20regions%20within%20the%20Ottoman%20Empire.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20wars%20is%20a%20little%20more%20complex.%20How%20can%20it%20be%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Arabs%20who%20started%20the%201948%20war%20when%20the%20deliberate%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Palestinians%20had%20already%20begun%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20already%20a%20secret%20deal%20between%20King%20Abdu