aloni%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20Post%20her%20marriage%20with%20IAS%20Ashish%20Vashishta%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20For%20their%20marriage%2C%20Saloni%20paid%20a%20court%20fee%20of%20Rs%20500%20and%20reported%20to%20work%20within%20two%20days.%20She%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20her%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202014-batch%20IAS%20officer%20shares%20her%20strategy%20for%20the%20first-time%20aspirants%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20not%20follow%20what%20everyone%20else%20does%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFigure%20out%20what%20works%20out%20best%20for%20you.%20You%20need%20to%20have%20a%20very%20customised%20approach%20for%20yourself.%20Some%20people%20prefer%20studying%20in%20groups%2C%20some%20prefer%20to%20study%20alone%20in%20a%20room.%20That%20is%20totally%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBe%20consistent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Saloni%20had%20roughly%20a%20year%20for%20preparation%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20her%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreparing%20for%20UPSC%20is%20not%20a%20100-metre%20race.%20It%20is%20a%20marathon.%20Here%2C%20you%20have%20to%20study%20for%20at%20least%20a%20whole%20year.%20You%20cannot%20have%20abrupt%20moments%20of%20very%20extensive%20study%20and%20then%20go%20into%20a%20shell%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saloni%20is%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-1-1700746934-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20is%20posted%20as%20the%20district%20collector%20of%20Mandla%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20aspirants%2C%20Saloni%20says%2C%20she%20was%20not%20obsessed%20with%20the%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20dedicated%20and%20sincere%20to%20my%20preparation%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20relaxed%20and%20not%20stressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20examination%20in%20the%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20Saloni%20says%2C%20was%20her%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20I%20would%20dedicate%20around%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20to%20preparation.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20day%20when%20I%20took%20an%20off.%20Usually%2C%20some%20people%20study%20for%2012%20hours%20one%20day%20and%20then%20waste%20time%20sleeping%20for%20the%20entire%20next%20day.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeek%20guidance%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20if%20you%20want%20to%20take%20support%20from%20coaching.%20Personally%2C%20I%20preferred%20joining%20a%20coaching%20institute%20where%20they%20had%20very%20less%20aspirants%2C%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20a%20class%20of%20400%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20had%20five%20months%20to%20appear%20for%20prelims.%20I%20would%20seclude%20myself%20in%20a%20library%2C%20away%20from%20the%20chaos%20of%20aspirants%20who%20keep%20advising%20others%20to%20follow%20this%20or%20that%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334807%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELive%20in%20your%20comfort%20zone%20a%20month%20before%20the%20exam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%20says%20that%20she%20moved%20to%20her%20comfort%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20her%20home%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20last%20month%20before%20appearing%20for%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not